{
  "page": "Dome",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Dome</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Mummer\" title=\"Mummer\">mummers</a> playhouse in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>.  It is rival to the <a href=\"/index.php/Gate_(playhouse)\" title=\"Gate (playhouse)\">Gate</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Blue_Lantern\" title=\"Blue Lantern\">Blue Lantern</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Mercy_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Mercy-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is located on the northern shore of the city, west of the <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_Harbor\" title=\"Purple Harbor\">Purple Harbor</a>, several blocks north of the <a href=\"/index.php/Canal_of_Heroes\" title=\"Canal of Heroes\">Canal of Heroes</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafbraavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafbraavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"About\">About</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dome&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: About\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Dome's environs are more fashionable than the <a href=\"/index.php/Gate_(playhouse)\" title=\"Gate (playhouse)\">Gate's</a> and its offerings are considered subtler and more poetic.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Mercy_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Mercy-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>During a performance at the Dome, someone once replaced one of the trick daggers with a real one and a mummer was killed during a performance.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Mercy_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Mercy-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Izembaro\" title=\"Izembaro\">Izembaro</a>, head of the mummers troupe from the Gate, had first dubbed himself the King of the Mummers, the Dome's mummers were outraged.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Mercy_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Mercy-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dome&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Mercy-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Mercy_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Mercy_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Mercy_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Mercy_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Mercy_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Mercy (The Winds of Winter)\">Mercy</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafbraavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafbraavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Braavos.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405004057\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.010 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 129/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8648/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 304/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 46/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function